OL,3,CEnergy crisis will define Holyrood
OL,4,Celection, says Flynn
OL,6,FSoaring energy bills will "define this
OL,7,FHolyrood election campaign", SNP
OL,8,FWestminster leader Stephen Flynn has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe MP ` who is a candidate in
OL,12,FAberdeen Deeside and North Kincardine
OL,13,F` was speaking ahead of a campaign
OL,14,Fvisit in Glasgow on Friday.
OL,16,FVoters, he said, will be casting their
OL,17,Fballots for "a permanent cost-of-
OL,18,Fliving crisis under Westminster or
OL,19,Flower energy bills with independence".
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@[O]yD@MOU{D@eO]
