OL,3,CEnergy crisis will define Holyrood
OL,4,Celection, says Flynn
OL,6,FMr Flynn said: "It is almost
OL,7,Finevitable that the deepening energy
OL,8,Fcrisis will come to define this
OL,9,FHolyrood election campaign ` voters
OL,10,Fwill rightly cast their verdict on why
OL,11,FWestminster's control of Scotland's
OL,12,Fenergy has left families and
OL,13,Fbusinesses paying some of the highest
OL,14,Fcosts in Europe.
OL,16,F"This election will boil down to a
OL,17,Fstraight choice for the people of
OL,18,FScotland ` a permanent cost-of-living
OL,19,Fcrisis under Westminster or lower
OL,20,Fenergy bills with independence.
OL,26,@nD@POUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
