OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774576986
OL,3,CEnergy crisis will define Holyrood
OL,4,Celection, says Flynn
OL,6,F"On May 7 voters can choose who is in
OL,7,Fcontrol of Scotland's energy ` the
OL,8,FWestminster establishment or the
OL,9,Fpeople of Scotland.
OL,11,F"Scottish voters haven't forgotten
OL,12,Fthat Keir Starmer, and his then
OL,13,Fsidekick Anas Sarwar, promised to cut
OL,14,Fenergy bills by #300 ` instead the
OL,15,FLabour Party's broken promises will
OL,16,Flikely mean that people will be hit
OL,17,Fwith bills that are #705 higher.
OL,19,F"With independence and full control
OL,20,Fover our energy resources, we can
OL,21,Fbring energy bills down.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
