CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774576986
OL,3,CEnergy crisis will define Holyrood
OL,4,Celection, says Flynn
OL,6,F"That only comes with the fresh start
OL,7,Fof independence ` and that is what
OL,8,Fonly the SNP can offer to the people
OL,9,Fof Scotland at this election."
OL,11,FBut Scottish Tory energy spokesman
OL,12,FDouglas Lumsden accused Mr Flynn of
OL,13,F"hypocrisy", also attacking the
OL,14,FScottish Government's presumption
OL,15,Fagainst oil and gas.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Government published its
OL,18,Fdraft energy strategy while Nicola
OL,19,FSturgeon was in office, which included
OL,20,Fthe policy which leaned away from
OL,21,Ffossil fuels.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]uD@AOUuD@KO]
