OL,3,CEnergy crisis will define Holyrood
OL,4,Celection, says Flynn
OL,6,FHowever, a final plan is yet to be
OL,7,Fpublished, leaving the Government's
OL,8,Fpolicy uncertain.
OL,10,F"Only this week SNP MPs as well as
OL,11,FLabour refused to back our common-
OL,12,Fsense motion in Westminster calling
OL,13,Ffor the UK Government to end their ban
OL,14,Fon new licences in the North Sea," Mr
OL,15,FLumsden said.
OL,17,F"Stephen Flynn is shamelessly trying
OL,18,Fto dupe voters in the north rast when
OL,19,Fhe knows full well that his party have
OL,20,Fdecimated the sector.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@bO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
