OL,3,CEnergy crisis will define Holyrood
OL,4,Celection, says Flynn
OL,6,F"The Scottish Conservatives are the
OL,7,Fonly party standing up for oil and gas
OL,8,Fworkers and backing North Sea drilling
OL,9,Fto cut energy bills for hard-pressed
OL,10,FScots ` that's why you need to vote
OL,11,Ffor us on your peach ballot to stop an
OL,12,FSNP majority."
OL,14,FScottish Labour deputy leader Dame
OL,15,FJackie Baillie said: "The SNP want to
OL,16,Fdo anything other than talk about
OL,17,Ftheir own dismal record in government.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]wD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
