OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774576986
OL,3,CEnergy crisis will define Holyrood
OL,4,Celection, says Flynn
OL,6,F"They want to talk about independence
OL,7,Fand the arguments of the past because
OL,8,Fthey do not have anything new to offer
OL,9,Fthe people of Scotland.
OL,11,F"Stephen Flynn elbowed women
OL,12,Fcandidates out of the way in his
OL,13,Fdesperate bid to become an MSP and is
OL,14,Feyeing up John Swinney's job next.
OL,16,F"Only Scottish Labour can defeat the
OL,17,FSNP and offer the people of Scotland
OL,18,Fthe opportunity to take a new
OL,19,Fdirection."
